name: A better wad i pulled out of my ass
description: A few weeks before this wad came out, someone released an awful mod called "Doom Rampage Edition", which, if youre reading this in 2010 is probably long forgotten, but trust me, it was terrible, anyway, after playing it i said "I could pull a better wad out of my ass", so went ahead and did so, DRE took 3 years, Mine took just over 3 weeks
